      "raw_text": "E. Christie, a Spokane & Inland\nbrakeman on a construction train,\nis lying at Sacred Heart hospital\nseriously injured as the result of\nbeing thrown against telegraph\npole when alighting from moving\ntrain. A portion of his jaw is torn\naway, teeth are knocked out and\nhis upper jaw is fractured. DR.. E.\nR. Northrop is attending him."
